panelsJSON.title: Audit Events by Verdict and Verdict Reason

params.markdown:
#### Island Browser

#### Overview

This dashboard provides visibility into audit events across the Island Browser platform, helping analysts track user and system activity.

Filters allow refinement by event type and verdict, while time-series charts highlight audit trends over time. Bar and pie charts break down events by verdict, verdict reason, type, OS platform, and compatibility mode. Tables showcase top rules, top users, and source IPs, while a map displays geographic distribution by source region.

An audit essentials panel with host, device, and source details provides quick context for monitoring and investigations.
